<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فانْصَرَفَتْ وهيَ حِصانُ مُغْضَبَةْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>ورَفَعَتْ بصَوْتِها هَيّا أبَهْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>